d prods from my friends and family who are quick to offer their opinions about how to solve my slight paunch. While I’m lucky in the sense that I am not overweight, I don’t consider myself healthy. I’m comically un-athletic, prone to moments of social anxiety and consistently frustrated by my wardrobe. Over the years of living with this Ford Taurus of a body, I’ve come to accept some things about myself that I urge all people—skinny-fat and beyond—to realize and move on.\n<h2>1. It\'s impossible to find a t-shirt that fits</h2>\n<h3>2.....</h3>\n[tt_btn link=\"http://www.supercompressor.com/culture/10-things-i-ve-come-to-accept-about-being-skinny-fat-male-body-issues\" target=\"_blank\"]Read the full list @ supercompressor.com[\\tt_btn]\n\n&nbsp;','10 THINGS ONLY SKINNY-FAT GUYS UNDERSTAND','','inherit','closed','closed','','142-autosave-v1','','','2015-09-10 16:53:59','2015-09-10 21:53:59','',142,'http://musclemetrics.zone/142-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(145,2,'2010-05-07 08:08:30','2010-05-07 13:08:30','<h3 id=\"title-node-55291\" class=\"title\"><span class=\"field-dek\">Swimming workouts burn fat, trim inches and help you get stronger, fitter and healthier than ever</span></h3>\r\n<section class=\"info\"><span class=\"byline-wrapper\"><span class=\"byline-role\">BY </span><span class=\"field-author\">SELENE YEAGER – </span></span><span class=\"date\">May 7, 2010</span></section><section class=\"info\"></section><section class=\"info\">A pool might not be the first place you think of going when you\'re looking to shape up and slim down—but perhaps it should be. No other workoutburns calories, boosts metabolism, and firms every muscle in your body (without putting stress on your joints) better than a swimming workout.Look no further than superstar Natalie Coughlin to observe how water can whittle a sexy, sculpted silhouette. And you don\'t have to be an Olympic gold medalist to get the perfect body. When researchers at Indiana University compared recreational fitness swimmers with non-swimmers, they found that swimmers of all ages had more lean muscle and trimmer waists and hips.And while swimming may not offer the lace-up-your-shoes-and-go convenience of running, all you need are three key items—swimsuit, cap, and goggles—and you\'re set to hit the water. So go ahead: Make a splash with one of the best workouts for women!\r\n\r\n</section><section class=\"info\"></section><section class=\"info\">[tt_btn link=\"http://www.womenshealthmag.com/fitness/swim-workout-0?cid=soc_WomensHealthMag_TWITTER_Women%27s+Health_\" target=\"_blank\"]Read the full article @ womenshealthmag.com[/tt_btn]</section>','Best Swimming Workout: Lose Body Fat in the Pool','','publish','open','open','','best-swimming-workout-lose-body-fat-in-the-pool','','','2015-09-10 17:57:01','2015-09-10 22:57:01','',0,'http://musclemetrics.zone/?p=145',0,'post','',0),(146,2,'2015-09-10 17:02:19','2015-09-10 22:02:19','','1006-swim-your-butt-off','','inherit','open','closed','','1006-swim-your-butt-off','','','2015-09-10 17:02:19','2015-09-10 22:02:19','',145,'http://musclemetrics.zone/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1006-swim-your-butt-off.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(147,2,'2015-09-10 17:21:02','2015-09-10 22:21:02','Athletic Testing Solutions (ATS) is a national provider of comprehensive heart screens for early detection of  cardiac health risks, The “ATS Heart Check”.  Having kids properly tested by ATS is the best defense against Sudden Cardiac Arrest.  Our comprehensive testing package includes Blood Pressure, Electrocardiogram (EKG) and Echocardiogram (Heart Imaging).  We work with board certified cardiologists, registered ultrasounds technicians and trained staff to bring the best screening experience possible right to your school or organization.\n\nThough Sudden Cardiac Arrest is often fatal, action can be taken to help prevent it.  Be proactive by evaluating symptoms and concerns and have your child tested today!\n\nAthletic Testing Solutions is 