tp://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?cmd=Retrieve&amp;dopt=AbstractPlus&amp;list_uids=15599731&amp;query_hl=2\" target=\"_blank\"]Read full article @ PubMed.gov[/tt_btn]\n\n</div>\n</div>','Can body volume be determined by PET?','','inherit','closed','closed','','134-autosave-v1','','','2015-09-10 18:21:20','2015-09-10 23:21:20','',134,'http://musclemetrics.zone/134-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(157,2,'2015-09-10 18:24:55','2015-09-10 23:24:55','','PubMed','','inherit','open','closed','','pubmed','','','2015-09-10 18:24:55','2015-09-10 23:24:55','',134,'http://musclemetrics.zone/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/PubMed.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(158,2,'2015-09-10 19:06:30','2015-09-11 00:06:30','On the road to strength, there are many paths we can choose. Barbells, dumbbells, or kettlebells? Elastic bands, medicine balls, or bulky machines? All of the above, or none? There are many conflicting views out there, but those familiar with my work know exactly where I stand: To get everything you want out of life and fitness, you don’t need much\r\n\r\nWherever your stance, it’s an indisputable fact that to get big and/or strong you must challenge your muscles against resistance. This is life. However, that resistance does not necessarily have to be an external object. In fact, your own body, the laws of gravity, and dear, sweet Mother Nature in her infinite splendor provide all the resistance you need to get stronger than you’ve ever been in your entire life.\r\n\r\nThis is how you get <i>strong</i> using body weight only. Here’s the straight dope, right from the heart. The voice of experience. Brace yourself, because it may not be what you’re used to hearing.\r\n\r\n[tt_btn link=\"http://workouttips.net/the-7-dos-and-donts-of-bodyweight-strength/\" target=\"_blank\"]Read all 7 Tips @ http://workouttips.net[/tt_btn]','The 7 Do’s And Don’ts Of Bodyweight Strength','','publish','open','open','','the-7-dos-and-donts-of-bodyweight-strength','','','2015-09-10 19:06:30','2015-09-11 00:06:30','',0,'http://musclemetrics.zone/?p=158',0,'post','',0),(159,2,'2015-09-10 19:06:01','2015-09-11 00:06:01','','push-ups','','inherit','open','closed','','push-ups','','','2015-09-10 19:06:01','2015-09-11 00:06:01','',158,'http://musclemetrics.zone/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/push-ups.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(160,2,'2015-06-30 08:08:37','2015-06-30 13:08:37','<blockquote>If exercise makes you smarter, I\'m going to workout so hard I\'ll become a genius!</blockquote>\r\n<h3>A new study finds that endurance sports like cycling may help prevent cognitive decline.</h3>\r\nBy Nelson Rice ( bicycling.com ), June 30, 2015\r\n\r\nHere’s more reason to keep riding well after you’ve eclipsed 40 years old:Endurance exercise may keep your brain working at full-tilt as you age, according to a new study in the journal <em>Medicine &amp; Science in Sports &amp; Exercise</em>.\r\n\r\nResearchers at the University of Texas at Austin attempted to determine the correlation between a person’s cardio fitness and cognitive function in middle-aged adults.\r\n\r\n[tt_btn link=\"http://www.bicycling.com/training/health-injuries/exercise-makes-you-smarter-you-age\" target=\"_blank\"]Read the full article @ bicycling.com[/tt_btn]','Exercise Makes You Smarter as You Age','','publish','open','open','','exercise-makes-you-smarter-as-you-age','','','2015-09-10 19:18:11','2015-09-11 00:18:11','',0,'http://musclemetrics.zone/?p=160',0,'post','',0),(161,2,'2015-09-10 19:15:30','2015-09-11 00:15:30','','brain','','inherit','open','closed','','brain','','','2015-09-10 19:15:30','2015-09-11 00:15:30','',160,'http://musclemetrics.zone/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/brain.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(162,2,'2015-09-11 11:27:41','2015-09-11 16:27:41','Originally published on Aug 6, 2014 by <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCK_XB33VOP0gi3Jk3UzObCQ\" data-sessionlink=\"itct=CDAQ4TkiEwj0oZnYsu_HAhVNAMsKHWL1B2Eo-B0\" data-ytid=\"UCK_XB33VOP0gi3Jk3UzObCQ\">DiscoverStrength</a> on YouTube\r\n\r\nA Bod Pod test measures the percentage of your body weight that is comprised of lean tissue versus fat tissue. When you gain or lose weight, a scale doesn\'t tell you if that weight change is muscle or fat. This test is the ultimate tool for tracking your progress because it reliably tells you how much lean muscle you have gained and how much fat you have lost.\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vZs5eiZOwNs?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>','BOD POD as the ultimate tool for tracking progress during strength training','','publish','open','open','','bod-pod-as-the-ultimate-tool-for-tracking-progress-during-strength-training','','','2015-09-11 11:29:16','2015-09-11 16:29:16','',0,'http://musclemetrics.zone/?p=162',0,'post','',0),(163,2,'2015-09-11 11:28:42','2015-09-11 16:28:42','','DiscoverStrength','','inherit','open','closed','','discoverstrength','','','2015-09-11 11:28:42','2015-09-11 16:28:42','',162,'http://musclemetrics.zone/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/DiscoverStrength.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(164,3,'2015-09-12 11:14:50','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-09-12 11:14:50','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://musclemetrics.zone/?p=164',0,'post','',0),(165,3,'2015-09-14 14:34:04','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2015-09-14 14:34:04','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://musclemetrics.zone/?page_id=165',0,'page','',0),(166,3,'2015-09-14 15:34:06','2015-09-14 20:34:06','October 10th, 2015\n\n[app_schedule date=\"2015-10-10\" wor]','Corporate Woods','','inherit','closed','closed','','87-autosave-v1','','','2015-09-14 15:34:06','2015-09-14 20:34:06','',87,'http://musclemetrics.zone/87-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(167,3,'2015-09-14 15:41:07','2015-09-14 20:41:07','<table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\">[app_my_appointments]</td></tr><tr><td>[app_services]</td><td>[app_servic